155e68683459c9fea9b97d8","tid":2323402,"uid":317651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"其實一直聽到環保撚講話有膠粒<br />\n但無人講如果食咗會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"就係冇人知會點<br />\n以前冇咁嘅現象<br />\n所以先驚"},{"pid":"a7be72a2d742504633298068fcc92526d3860d35","tid":2323402,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e43664129cb4ee19a155e68683459c9fea9b97d8","tid":2323402,"uid":317651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"其實一直聽到環保撚講話有膠粒<br />\n但無人講如果食咗會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"其實對人嘅傷害嘅相關研究仲做緊<br />\n德國 最近研究就講佢哋搵到當地嘅細路體內已經有一定數量嘅microplastic<br />\n 同埋microplastics有太多種類 衣物纖維都可以係其中一種 所以研究需時"},{"pid":"d55119cfe83b1c66ce8d5389ab7520a422a541b9","tid":2323402,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"仲有啲研究講BB沖熱奶的時候，chok樽的動作都有機會產生啲microplastic<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9e7660c303f3d055eb1f9fad4be4af14ddbe51","tid":2323402,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d55119cfe83b1c66ce8d5389ab7520a422a541b9","tid":2323402,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"仲有啲研究講BB沖熱奶的時候，chok樽的動作都有機會產生啲microplastic<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"如果講到咁細單位<br />\n根本所有有膠嘅容器<br />\n都會有膠甩出黎，或者溶喺食物度<br />\n<br />\n所以有啲好介意嘅人先會堅持用玻璃"},{"pid":"785b1231c373cb7770c19b29e78142202430cf00","tid":2323402,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"好似石棉咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有以後好多唔同種類嘅粒粒都會畀人咁scrutinize"},{"pid":"7eaa449ce10d2411258092085ed545f990d81ece","tid":2323402,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:19:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"limegreen\">另外下次薯仔可唔可以討論下支那滅活疫苗,   會唔會導致用者核酸測試呈陽性比人捉十四日</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似冇人討論過呢個比較有科學根據嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大部分討論都圍繞住副作用/產地/反唔反共/陰毛論"}]}